metadata.name: The Ancients of Egypt
metadata.description:
We have traversed the vast oceans of space and time to share our knowledge, grow our population, and spread our culture so that we may ultimately save it. We have expanded your minds and provided you the tools to create new worlds of your own. We have secretly paved the way for your greatest achievments. We are the spark that ignites your dreams to make them your reality. We are The Ancients. We are travelers from the stars.

3840 x 2160
